<p>
	
</p>
<div id="player">
	<i id="ttttt">14441</i>
</div>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<strong>今天的话题是：几道让外国人恶心的中国菜</strong><strong></strong>
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;">
	<strong><img src="/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/20161028170659_99743.gif" alt="" /><br />
</strong>
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;">
	<strong><img src="/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/20161028170714_63194.jpg" alt="" /><br />
</strong>
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;">
	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;大家好， hello， 我最近又发现了一个问题，美国人讨厌中国菜。
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;">
	<img src="/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/20161028170748_71620.jpg" alt="" />
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;">
	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;I went to a restaurant yesterday with some friends, 昨天跟一帮朋友在外边吃饭， 知了上桌了。
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;">
	<img src="/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/20161028170836_27266.jpg" alt="" />
</p>
<p>
	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;其中一个男的， 说what the fuck is that, Chinese eat bugs? Do you like bug’s shit in the mouth？中国人吃虫子吗？喜欢它们的屎，它们所有的东西嚼在嘴里？
</p>
<p>
	<img src="/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/20161028170907_62041.jpg" alt="" />
</p>
<p>
	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;我说，这个很好吃，特别香，有这个蛋白质，特别好吃。
</p>
<p>
	<img src="/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/20161028171002_30970.jpg" alt="" />
</p>
<p>
	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;另外一个男的说， Are those, are those feet? Those are feet, what ,why, you guys eat feet? 中国人吃脚吗？
</p>
<p>
	<img src="/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/20161028171112_68485.jpg" alt="" />
</p>
<p>
	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;我说这个是猪蹄，特别好吃，pig’s feet, very good for you, 煮的，煮的很烂，特别香 really good.
</p>
<p>
	<img src="/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/20161028171204_26017.jpg" alt="" />
</p>
<p>
	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Then there is a girl, she sees the fish, the fish ,the fish, fish’s eyes is looking at me, I can do it, it’s ok, I can do it , I can do it , I can do it.<span style="line-height:1.5;">我可以吃一点吗，我来，我来，我来，我来，我来，我说你吃个鱼，都吃到高潮了。</span>
</p>
<p>
	<span style="line-height:1.5;"><img src="/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/20161028171325_47779.jpg" alt="" /><br />
</span>
</p>
<p>
	<span style="line-height:1.5;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Americans, what do they have to eat? 美国有什么好吃的？汉堡，牛排。</span>
</p>
<p>
	<span style="line-height:1.5;"><img src="/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/20161028171449_69020.jpg" alt="" /><br />
</span>
</p>
<p>
	<span style="line-height:1.5;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;没有文化，教你们一句话， 吃文化， 美国没有吃文化， 懂吗？ Bye-bye.<br />
</span>
</p>
<p>
	<span style="line-height:1.5;"><br />
</span>
</p>
<p>
	<span style="line-height:1.5;"><img src="/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/20161028171955_34120.jpg" alt="" /><br />
</span>
</p>
<p>
	<span style="line-height:1.5;"><br />
</span>
</p>
<p>
	<span style="line-height:1.5;"> </span>
</p>
<p>
	<img src="http://wz.chinesecio.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/20160920121426_94455.jpg" alt="" />
</p>
