				<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal">
	
</p>
<p>
	<img src="http://wz.chinesecio.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/20160920121426_94455.jpg" alt="" />
</p>
<div id="player">
	<i id="ttttt">14431</i>
</div>
<p style="text-align:left;">
	<strong><br />
</strong>
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<strong>今天的话题是：老外第一次在中国检查眼睛要笑疯了</strong>
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;">
	<strong><img src="/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/20161026135427_25879.gif" alt="" /><br />
</strong>
</p>
<p>
	&nbsp;&nbsp;<img src="/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/20161026110227_54962.jpg" alt="" width="554" height="312" title="" align="" />&nbsp;&nbsp;
</p>
<p>
	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Hello, 大家好。 So my first time giving my eyes checked in China.第一次在中国检查眼睛</p>
<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<img src="/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/20161026110250_48221.jpg" alt="" width="554" height="312" title="" align="" />
</p>
<p>
	<span style="line-height:1.5;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;The doctor told me coming. 医生说进来.And she said sit here, I’m going to ask you some question 她说，你坐这， 我要问你几个问题。</span>
</p>
<p>
	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<img src="/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/20161026110317_73092.jpg" alt="" width="554" height="312" title="" align="" />
</p>
<p>
	&nbsp;&nbsp;I said, ok, 我说，好， 然后她指着那个东西。
</p>
<p>
	&nbsp;&nbsp;<img src="/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/20161026110337_13791.jpg" alt="" width="554" height="312" title="" align="" />&nbsp;
</p>
<p>
	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;She pointed at that thing, and she asked me questions. 然后我直接回答了。
</p>
<p>
	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<img src="/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/20161026110350_88508.jpg" alt="" width="554" height="312" title="" align="" />&nbsp;
</p>
<p>
	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;And then the doctor and my girlfriend, they were both laughing at me. 然后我女朋友和医生，两个人都笑疯了。
</p>
<p>
	&nbsp; &nbsp;<img src="/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/20161026110404_68655.jpg" alt="" width="554" height="312" title="" align="" />
</p>
<p>
	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;I didn’t know what’s going on, I didn’t understand. 我不懂。
</p>
<p>
	&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;I&nbsp; told them, I said isn’t it supposed to be to be M and E? What’s wrong? 我说难道那个不是念的是M和E吗？
</p>
<p>
	<img src="http://wz.chinesecio.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/20161026110415_77742.jpg" alt="" width="554" height="312" title="" align="" /><span style="line-height:1.5;">&nbsp;</span>
</p>
<p>
	&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;And then the doctor, it’s like , up, , left, right down, 上下左右
</p>
<p>
	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<img src="http://wz.chinesecio.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/20161026110425_12217.jpg" alt="" width="554" height="312" title="" align="" />
</p>
<p>
	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;And then , she asked me a question, she said what if this is M , and this is E, what about this one? I said, it should be 3, 然后她说，那如果是这样的话， 这个是E， 这个是M， 那这个呢，应该怎么说呢？ 我说3呐，应该是3<br />
<span style="line-height:1.5;"><br />
</span>
</p>
<p>
	<span style="line-height:1.5;"><img src="/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/20161026110637_84732.jpg" alt="" width="554" height="312" title="" align="" /><br />
</span>
</p>
<p>
	<span style="line-height:1.5;">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;And the doctor, just hahaha , ok, bye-bye, au revoir, adios, 再见。</span>
</p>
<p>
	<img src="http://wz.chinesecio.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/20161026113220_81595.jpg" alt="" />
</p>
<p>
	
</p>
<p>
	<img src="http://wz.chinesecio.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/20160920121426_94455.jpg" alt="" />
</p>
